TASK 1:

mkdir to make directories
cd to change directories
touch to create a file
cp to copy files
ls -a to list the hidden files and folders


TASK 2:

sudo dnf install htop:
 to install the htop

htop:
 to use the htop i.e. to see the process and it's cpu consumption and such

dnf list installed | grep nginx:
 to check whether nginx is installed or not

dnf list installed > listPackages.txt:
 to list all the packages installed and direct the output to the listPackages.txt file